{"tid":583434,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"點解一念無名票房咁好？","createTime":"2018-03-07T03:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T15:26:20.000Z","uid":167457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"15920b0d1b3124551b7450a2d897b0541a2a6b1a","tid":583434,"uid":167457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"呢排見到大樂師票房咁慘淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n突然諗起一念無明<br />\n雖然自己都好鍾意一念無明 但就唔明佢有咩突圍而出 會有咁高票房<br />\n如果講卡士 以青春的名義應該不相伯仲？兩者都係首部劇情 但以青春票房都係麻麻<br />\n如果講片種突破 大樂師係香港少有既音樂片 但大樂師同樣下場 <br />\n大家都係誠意之作 到底一念無名有咩咁特別？<br />\n虛心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：以上全部都鍾意"},{"pid":"55dd324235666ebc80fd99549dbe876c05e3698f","tid":583434,"uid":41343,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:54:40.000Z","msg":"上映前要靠媒體煲起個話題"},{"pid":"ff1191d07858d1db670d287a855af58ce82a009a","tid":583434,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"大樂師淨係fb間唔中先見到廣告 點夠宣傳呀"},{"pid":"b0aa3080aa527359a4e5c890dda8117dbd7cb288","tid":583434,"uid":167457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"55dd324235666ebc80fd99549dbe876c05e3698f","tid":583434,"uid":41343,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:54:40.000Z","msg":"上映前要靠媒體煲起個話題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"姐係佢其實只係贏左係宣傳位上？"},{"pid":"e9fbff5a989b17b1f757d8647961e9f0c9a41d92","tid":583434,"uid":1670,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"香港上映前已經拎左金馬獎？"},{"pid":"b99f76e64bdcd4f2bba38dff1b825da9e8122411","tid":583434,"uid":36481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"因為條trailer唔吸引<br />\n顏卓靈啲戲又屎"},{"pid":"6df30e9a93f154738f5995cba7c3bd1afd9136ab","tid":583434,"uid":41343,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b0aa3080aa527359a4e5c890dda8117dbd7cb288","t